Text:
A one-use neural inoculation which trains a specific cryptic revelation.

The dose is administered through a specialized implant point. Once released into the brain, the mechanism forms knowledge of a specific revelation, transmuting itself into neural tissue as needed.

{PSYCAST_label}

{PSYCASTDESCRIPTION}

These guests can't afford to claim a suite:

{0}
Provide cheaper or complimentary suites or gift the guests some silver. Better-connected factions tend to arrive with fuller purses.

These guests have nothing to eat:

{0}
Put food on sale, stock a refreshment kiosk, or gift the guests some silver or rations. You can also allow guests to dine for free.

You’ve just received a proposition from {0} of {1}. They have a surplus of prisoners at one of their holdings and are looking to offload a few for a fee.

{0} says that two batches are available for transfer - one low-security, the other high-security. If you accept, both the payment and the prisoners will be transferred to you by vertibird.

Low-sec payment: {2}
High-sec payment: {3}

